title: Nick Swardson

description:
Nick Swardson (RENO 911, THE DO-OVER, BUDDY GAMES) is on the pod this week and relentlessly roasts Whitney.  He also shares hilarious stories about touring with friends Adam Sandler, David Spade, and Norm MacDonald.  Check out http://nickswardson.net/ for all things Nick.
